we are a core division...

676
00:49:59,710 --> 00:50:02,168
...that both manages
and supports the company.

677
00:50:02,377 --> 00:50:03,710
Oh, that's right.

678
00:50:04,168 --> 00:50:05,252
Core division.

679
00:50:06,377 --> 00:50:09,918
I hope we can bring you both on board
