681
00:50:12,210 --> 00:50:13,751
My desk!

682
00:50:15,085 --> 00:50:17,293
Here are your intern badges.

683
00:50:17,626 --> 00:50:20,168
Lee Seolbi, your picture came out well.

684
00:50:22,543 --> 00:50:24,252
-Please don't lose this.
-Thank you very much!

685
00:50:27,460 --> 00:50:28,626
"Kim Hyejin"

686
00:50:30,460 --> 00:50:31,584
My work badge!

687
00:50:32,710 --> 00:50:34,168
-Miss Kim Hyejin?
-Yes!

688
00:50:37,210 --> 00:50:38,377
