About 500 metres away is
a place called Woori Market.

698
00:51:04,500 --> 00:51:05,793
They've worked with us for many years.

699
00:51:05,876 --> 00:51:08,543
They give us 10 percent discount,
so go there.

700
00:51:10,460 --> 00:51:11,668
Thank you very much!

701
00:51:12,500 --> 00:51:15,460
Buy the gift cards as gifts
at the post office.

702
00:51:15,584 --> 00:51:18,793
Oh, and can you pay
my utility bill while you're there?

703
00:51:20,168 --> 00:51:23,085
Energy conservation campaigns
are our responsibility, too.

704
00:51:23,543 --> 00:51:25,584
