809
00:57:38,419 --> 00:57:40,419
-No we haven't.
-Did we meet at a club?

810
00:57:42,584 --> 00:57:45,002
I was wondering why I have to do this...

811
00:57:45,085 --> 00:57:46,127
Did you complete the translations?

812
00:57:46,210 --> 00:57:47,668
What? Oh, right.

813
00:57:48,501 --> 00:57:49,460
Right here.

814
00:57:50,210 --> 00:57:51,127
Thanks again.

815
00:57:52,419 --> 00:57:53,377
Yes.

816
00:57:55,377 --> 00:57:57,543
I'm curious. Why is everyone...

817
00:57:57,626 --> 00:58:00,335
Go to the cafe on the first floor
and take coffee to the studio.

818
00:58:00,918 --> 00:58:02,710
The first floor of
the building across from here.

819
00:58:03,668 --> 00:58:04,626
Wait.

820
00:58:27,377 --> 00:58:29,210
What's this place about?

821
00:58:34,960 --> 00:58:36,793
Now, we'll take 10!

822
00:58:37,252 --> 00:58:38,168
Coffee.

823
00:58:38,918 --> 00:58:40,210
Where is my coffee?

824
00:58:40,835 --> 00:58:42,626
The coffee is here!

825
00:58:46,252 --> 00:58:47,668
I'm so sorry.

826
00:58:48,793 --> 00:58:50,751
My apologies. I'm late, aren't I?

827
00:58:51,210 --> 00:58:52,835
I was involved in
a car accident on the way here.

828
00:58:52,916 --> 00:58:54,043
Who are you?

829
00:58:54,460 --> 00:58:55,460
What?

830
00:58:56,421 --> 00:58:59,043
I'm the new editing freelancer.

831
00:58:59,332 --> 00:59:00,252
What?

832
00:59:02,002 --> 00:59:03,460
Then who was that frizzy hair?

833
00:59:03,835 --> 00:59:06,793
She completed
the translations without any errors.

834
00:59:06,960 --> 00:59:09,127
I had her proof-read my documents, too.

835
00:59:09,500 --> 00:59:10,793
And she did a great job.

836
00:59:10,876 --> 00:59:12,419
Who on earth is she then?

837
00:59:18,168 --> 00:59:19,085
Oh, no!

838
00:59:19,168 --> 00:59:20,960
Stop! Mister!

839
00:59:21,835 --> 00:59:24,293
"Management Support Department"
What? The Most Editing Department?

840
00:59:24,807 --> 00:59:27,918
Why am I being reassigned there?

841
00:59:28,002 --> 00:59:30,587
They've requested your transfer.

842
00:59:30,668 --> 00:59:34,043
Ask them for the details,
and return here after three months.

843
00:59:34,127 --> 00:59:36,377
What? For three months?

844
00:59:37,751 --> 00:59:39,876
But I'm prepared to do my best
here at Management Support.

845
00:59:39,960 --> 00:59:41,751
You can do that when you get back.

846
00:59:41,835 --> 00:59:43,377
Just go.

847
00:59:43,710 --> 00:59:46,210
The Most Editing Department
is the most influential department.

848
00:59:46,293 --> 00:59:47,793
We do whatever they demand.

849
00:59:47,876 --> 00:59:49,335
If you do a great job over there...

850
00:59:49,584 --> 00:59:51,710
...it'll help you
land a full-time position here.

851
00:59:52,252 --> 00:59:53,293
But...

852
01:00:05,876 --> 01:00:07,127
Excuse me.

853
01:00:07,918 --> 01:00:09,377
So you've arrived?

854
01:00:11,377 --> 01:00:12,960
Have a seat over there.

855
01:00:13,085 --> 01:00:14,501
-Over there?
-Yes.

856
01:00:15,043 --> 01:00:16,210
I look forward to working with you.

857
01:00:16,500 --> 01:00:17,377
Yes.

858
01:00:22,043 --> 01:00:23,085
She's here.

859
01:00:23,419 --> 01:00:25,127
I know I've seen her somewhere before.

860
01:00:25,584 --> 01:00:26,626
What?

861
01:00:32,751 --> 01:00:35,252
I know I've seen her someplace before.

862
01:00:37,419 --> 01:00:38,460
Yes, Hari.

863
01:00:38,584 --> 01:00:40,002
What was your text about?

864
01:00:40,584 --> 01:00:42,043
Why were you transferred?

865
01:00:42,127 --> 01:00:43,210
I don't know.

866
01:00:43,626 --> 01:00:45,377
I don't know what's going on.

867
01:00:45,460 --> 01:00:46,835
Buongiorno!

868
01:00:46,918 --> 01:00:48,793
-Have you arrived?
-How are you today?

869
01:00:50,960 --> 01:00:52,168
Ciao!

870
01:00:53,127 --> 01:00:55,210
The weather is wonderful outside!

871
01:00:55,293 --> 01:00:56,168
Goodness!

872
01:00:56,460 --> 01:00:59,210
Hey, an amazing lady just walked in.

873
01:00:59,710 --> 01:01:06,710
Sometimes, reality hits us
without any warning.

874
01:01:06,960 --> 01:01:08,793
That's the guy from the elevator!

875
01:01:08,960 --> 01:01:10,710
I hate that guy!

876
01:01:11,168 --> 01:01:15,210
Is he here yet?
I thought he's coming today.

877
01:01:15,835 --> 01:01:19,460
That's why you must
always be on your toes.

878
01:01:20,085 --> 01:01:21,419
Oh, there he is now.

879
01:01:21,793 --> 01:01:25,127
Something you couldn't prepare for.

880
01:01:28,293 --> 01:01:29,460
Attention!

881
01:01:29,793 --> 01:01:31,002
Allow me to introduce to you.

882
01:01:31,710 --> 01:01:36,668
He's the deputy chief editor
transferred from our New York branch.

883
01:01:38,500 --> 01:01:39,501
Hello, Kim Hyejin?

884
01:01:40,210 --> 01:01:41,127
Hey!

885
01:01:41,710 --> 01:01:43,500
Oh, right!

886
01:01:44,210 --> 01:01:45,377
Michael Jackson!

887
01:01:45,500 --> 01:01:46,434
It's a pleasure to meet you.

888
01:01:46,626 --> 01:01:49,960
I'm your deputy chief editor,
Ji Sungjoon.

889
01:01:50,147 --> 01:01:52,377
None of us saw this coming.

890
01:01:52,960 --> 01:01:54,751
-This was the beginning...
-This was the beginning...

891
01:01:54,835 --> 01:01:57,127
...of our very own picture puzzle.

892
01:02:13,002 --> 01:02:14,293
"She Was Pretty"

893
01:02:14,419 --> 01:02:15,584
Allow me to introduce you.

894
01:02:15,793 --> 01:02:16,793
I'm Ji Sungjoon.

895
01:02:17,335 --> 01:02:18,210
Nice to meet you.

896
01:02:18,293 --> 01:02:21,293
Then you'll have to
face Ji Sungjoon every day?

897
01:02:21,501 --> 01:02:23,460
Hey, what if he recognizes me?

898
01:02:23,793 --> 01:02:25,835
This will be our first meeting.

899
01:02:25,918 --> 01:02:28,500
Out, out, out...

900
01:02:28,751 --> 01:02:29,793
Do you have a screw loose?

901
01:02:29,876 --> 01:02:32,501
There's no reason for us
to take this abuse!

902
01:02:32,835 --> 01:02:34,876
I thought it was your wish to work late?

903
01:02:35,127 --> 01:02:37,626
So why are you resigning
over something like that?

904
01:02:37,710 --> 01:02:39,168
I'm sorry.

905
01:02:39,293 --> 01:02:42,043
Did you think you could fool me forever?

906
01:02:47,252 --> 01:02:48,168
"She Was Pretty"

907
01:02:50,252 --> 01:02:54,419
"She Was Pretty"
